OL,6,FA woman whose daughter and two
OL,7,Fgrandchildren were murdered in their
OL,8,Fhome has started making care packages
OL,9,Ffor domestic abuse survivors.
OL,11,FAngela Smith's daughter Terri Harris,
OL,12,Fgrandson John Paul Bennett, who was
OL,13,F13, and granddaughter Lacey Bennett,
OL,14,F11, were two and half years ago, along
OL,15,Fwith Lacey's friend Connie Gent.
OL,17,FBendall, who had a history of
OL,18,Fviolence, was known by the authorities
OL,19,Fto be a risk to women and children
OL,20,Fwhen he moved in with Terri at her
OL,21,Fhome in Killamarsh near .
