OL,6,F"They're all hitting milestone
OL,7,Fbirthdays - my grandson would have
OL,8,Fbeen 16 in December."
OL,10,FFrom a small office in Killamarsh,
OL,11,FAngela is now making care packages for
OL,12,Fwomen fleeing domestic violence to
OL,13,Fdistribute to refuges across the
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,16,FContaining small essentials from
OL,17,Ftoothpaste to shower gel, they are a
OL,18,Fsmall gesture which could make a big
OL,19,Fdifference to those left with very
OL,20,Flittle.
