OL,3,CGrandmother supporting abuse survivors
OL,4,Cin memory of murdered children
OL,6,F"It's just so they've got that little
OL,7,Fbag, because a lot of these women
OL,8,Fleave with nothing," she said.
OL,10,F"Just so they've got something that's
OL,11,Ftheirs and to know that someone cares
OL,12,Fabout them.
OL,14,F"I just hope it makes someone smile."
OL,16,FThe bags are tagged with a heart and a
OL,17,Fmessage that reads 'With love from
OL,18,FTerri's Fight'.
