OL,6,FThe organisation was set up by Angela
OL,7,Fand family member Jade Donovan in an
OL,8,Feffort to help those affected by
OL,9,Fdomestic violence.
OL,11,FOver the course of a few weeks, they
OL,12,Fhave supplied 150 bags to various
OL,13,Fsupport groups.
OL,15,F"We want to support every woman who
OL,16,Fneeds that little bit of help," Jade
OL,17,Fsaid.
