OL,6,F"It's really sad that women are going
OL,7,Fthrough this every single day - it's
OL,8,Flovely for us to help, but sad that
OL,9,Fthis is even happening in the first
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,F"But if we can continue growing then
OL,13,Fthat's what we'll do."
OL,15,FTheir mission has already outgrown
OL,16,FAngela's kitchen where she began
OL,17,Fmaking the bags.
