OL,6,FThe community within Killamarsh, so
OL,7,Fhorrified by the deaths of Terri, John
OL,8,FPaul, Lacey and Connie, has rallied to
OL,9,Fdonate goods and the office space
OL,10,Fwhere Terri's Fight is now based.
OL,12,F"Everyone in Killamarsh has been
OL,13,Famazing, people on the website -
OL,14,Fwithout them this wouldn't have even
OL,15,Fbeen a thing," Angela said.
OL,17,FJade added: "People go on the Facebook
OL,18,Fpage and they find our wish list which
OL,19,Fthey donate to and it comes straight
OL,20,Fto us.
