OL,6,F"But if anyone wants to get in touch
OL,7,Fthey can also do that through the page
OL,8,Fand we'll talk to them about how they
OL,9,Fcan help us.
OL,11,F"We wanted to make positive change in
OL,12,FTerri's name, to make her continue
OL,13,Fhelping people because that's all she
OL,14,Fwanted to do in life," she said. "And
OL,15,Fshe would have loved it."
OL,17,FAngela says her grandchildren would
OL,18,Fhave been amazed to see her taking on
OL,19,Fthe role she has.
